            <abstract id="ref2" label="Abstract">The Kings County Almshouse was established in 1830. Included is a questionnaire answered by Almshouse officials with statistics on the institution for the year 1864, including land acreage and buildings, name of the authority in charge (the Board of Superintendents for the Poor), the number of inmates in residence at the Almshouse (including children), and yearly maintenance costs.</abstract>
